{"tid":873013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖過三和－毛坦廠","createTime":"2018-10-23T06:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T06:58:59.000Z","uid":31397,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"992479465e81e1bf3d56ba090e217a550779eb50","tid":873013,"uid":31397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:37:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WAmtH91S2GQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWAmtH91S2GQ&d=eZhh%2FlkBQm7FVMHtmBahcp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f7519323\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WAmtH91S2GQ</a><br />\n<br />\n震撼而又可悲<br />\n<br />\n毛坦廠鎮位於中國安徽省六安市金安區，毛坦廠鎮總面積59.6平方公里，總人口35096人。毛坦廠鎮轄7個村，1個社區。「毛坦廠」為「茅灘場」的諧音。名勝古蹟有毛坦廠明清老街等。<br />\n<br />\n中國教育界聞名遐邇的毛坦廠中學即位於本鎮，近20年來「毛中現象」成為高中教育研究和高考制度研究的熱門話題。"},{"pid":"b2e6732b191f46b9d21678d7e9d28d61ec44a915","tid":873013,"uid":196326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:44:38.000Z","msg":"其實就係機器將一個又一個學生壓成一模一樣 再掉返出嚟 壓唔成功嘅就話係失敗 佢哋自己都係咁樣諗 但一樣咁多人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649bf3613b6f69b61621a58e8b8a8ceb74d5fb5f","tid":873013,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"eb6af5a4cadc564aa6a9948f194ee9b249269cbd","tid":873013,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:48:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78ebcf374de12398febae778acbc339802d854fa","tid":873013,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b3529bc389c8bfc30bab9bc750407f8acad5579","tid":873013,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"雙非快去"},{"pid":"9a432eb1c59088ce2a503406e2272e225935e5de","tid":873013,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T06:58:59.000Z","msg":"關香港咩事"}]}